guys,. I'm sorry to come here out of nowhere but I just wanna say thank you. I'm multistan (I'm also Once but not hardstan yet) and now one of my group, ONEUS, is having a comeback with 'Black Mirror'. I knew that some of you have come to visit us, I often see that ONCE also comment there and show their support for our boys. so here I really wanna say thank you for that cuz it really means a lot for us. And now we're struggling to v0t3 on Starpass app cuz it's the only show we have chance to win and its been 2 years but they didn't get any wins yet we're still small fandom. I can't lie that I don't want your help to v0te but I don't want to force it again, cuz you've been helping us with the vw (but If you want, I'll be very grateful). so yeah, that's all. Thank you so much. goodluck for the next comeback! I heard that twice gonna make cb next month(?) I'm waiting for it too~ have a nice day everyone!

*sorry bad english
